\p ―Jna jaain²¹ 'in ngɨ¹ to² 'oo¹o fu coon²¹ lɨ jo 'in tsá² seein²¹, jna fuu²¹²uu tsá²: “'Ná²‑a ná³ coon²¹ fu¹ coon²¹ tsáa¹ tya' Ña'ñʉ'¹ʉ'” ―gajin'² Wó³ do. La nigajin'² 'in tsá² 'in gacwo¹ júu³ tya' Dios calɨɨ 'in sii²¹ Isaías. 
