\v 10 Pe mo ngayuui'¹³ gangalíin²in ruu'²¹i Jesús, Jesús gangó¹o cɨɨn²¹mo fu lɨ tɨ jmɨɨ²¹² do. 'Uun²¹mo tyíi¹a, jo gangɨɨ¹ɨ jee²¹² tsá².  
\v 11 Joon 'in tsá² Israel do 'áa¹mo 'naa'¹i 'ido 'ii jee²¹² lɨ tɨ jmɨɨ²¹². Jin'²in: 
\p ―¿Xiiafu tyee'¹i 'in tsañʉʉ'¹ no? 
